  <Lines>k__BackingField:
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c468415a02cbf74438a48816b0fe1fa6, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3973df86522e4b743879172e3518e737, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - " Vous n\u2019avez jamais fait de commande avant ?"
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c468415a02cbf74438a48816b0fe1fa6, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f0358eca1d351f540a61dc689202b2b8, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Les retards diminuent \xE9norm\xE9ment notre paie, c\u2019est hors de question
      !"
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c468415a02cbf74438a48816b0fe1fa6, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3973df86522e4b743879172e3518e737, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Je suis s\xFBre qu\u2019il l\u2019a fait expr\xE8s, pour qu\u2019on soit en
      retard et qu\u2019il aie \xE0 moins nous payer, quelle pince de crabe !\r\n"
